Title: cmk option --plugins does not work with -i
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1614967070
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p1

The commandline option <tt>--plugins</tt> was not working
in conjuction with the <tt>-i</tt> option. The selected
inventory plugins were not executed, resulting in a no-op.
